{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/victim-esports-jadi-tempat-gamer-belajar/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Victim Esports Ingin Jadi Tempat Gamer Pro Belajar dan Berkembang","content":"\n<p>Di usianya yang belum genap satu tahun, Victim Esports telah berhasil menorehkan beberapa prestasi yang cukup mengagumkan. Lihat saja di <a href=\"https://www.bola.com/e-sports/read/4041422/timnas-mobile-legends-indonesia-gagal-menjuarai-turnamen-independence-cup-2019\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Independence Cup (opens in a new tab)\">Independence Cup</a> tanggal 17-18 Agustus lalu, dimana tim Mobile Legends mereka berhasil menjadi juara dengan mengalahkan Timnas A dan Timnas B hasil bentukan Pelatnas SEA Games 2019.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"55416\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/victim-esports-jadi-tempat-gamer-belajar/attachment/01-victim-esports/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/01-victim-esports.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-victim-esports\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/01-victim-esports-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/01-victim-esports.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/01-victim-esports.jpg\" alt=\"Tim Mobile Legends Victim Esports pemenang Independence Cup. Sumber: CIAYO Pictures\" class=\"wp-image-55416\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/01-victim-esports.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/01-victim-esports-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Tim Mobile Legends Victim Esports pemenang Independence Cup. Sumber: CIAYO Pictures</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Pada tanggal 23 Agustus lalu di CGV FX Sudirman, tim Victim Esports menggelar acara “syukuran” sekaligus memperkenalkan anggota tim Esports yang berdiri tanggal 10 September 2018 lalu. Mereka terdiri dari beberapa tim yang berlaga di beberapa cabang game seperti PUBG, Mobile Legends, Free Fire, hingga Auto Chess. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Selain itu, mereka juga dibantui oleh empat orang brand ambassador yaitu Lalajo Laura, Dea Marella, KameAam, serta Natasha Caroline. Mereka merupakan Youtuber serta cosplayer yang terlibat dalam perkembangan esports di Indonesia.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Baca Juga: <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/kai-esports-exhibition-komitmen-pt-kai-rangkul-milenial/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">KAI Esports Exhibition: Komitmen KAI Rangkul Milenial</a></strong></p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"55417\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/victim-esports-jadi-tempat-gamer-belajar/attachment/02-victim-esports/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/02-victim-esports.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-victim-esports\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/02-victim-esports-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/02-victim-esports.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/02-victim-esports.jpg\" alt=\"Rickel Albert, manager tim Mobile Legends. Sumber: CIAYO Pictures\" class=\"wp-image-55417\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/02-victim-esports.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/02-victim-esports-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Rickel Albert, manager tim Mobile Legends. Sumber: CIAYO Pictures</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Meskipun berhasil mengalahkan tim bentukan Pelatnas, mereka tidak serta merta menyatakan diri sebagai semacam giant killer atau tim Los Galacticos. “Kita berawal dari pemain-pemain yang ingin berkembang, lalu bergabung menjadi satu, kita campur semua, sampai akhirnya menjadi seperti sekarang, tim yang berprestasi,” ungkap Rickel Albert selaku manajer tim Mobile Legends Victim Esports yang mengantar timnya menjuarai Independence Cup.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Hal yang sama juga diamini oleh CEO Victim Esports, Doni\nSetiawan. “Kita memang strateginya adalah mencari talenta-talenta baru, ambil\ndari semi-pro. Lalu kita didik, ajarin attitude dan juga cara bermain, supaya\npemain ini menjadi pemain yang matang,” jelasnya.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"55418\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/victim-esports-jadi-tempat-gamer-belajar/attachment/03-victim-esports/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/03-victim-esports.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-victim-esports\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/03-victim-esports-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/03-victim-esports.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/03-victim-esports.jpg\" alt=\"Hafiz Rachman Fauzi, general manager Victim Esports. Sumber: CIAYO Pictures\" class=\"wp-image-55418\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/03-victim-esports.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/03-victim-esports-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Hafiz Rachman Fauzi selaku general manager. Sumber: CIAYO Pictures</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>&#8220;Kita ingin terus berpartisipasi di semua kejuaraan.\nKami ingin membuat prestasi baru. Gelar Independence Cup masih belum\napa-apa,&#8221; lanjut GM Victim Esports Hafiz Rachman Fauzi. Sebagai bukti,\nagenda Victim Esports selanjutnya adalah pertandingan di negeri Jiran Malaysia.</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"0681c325-6401-5929-b651-12508c431c67"}}}